WHAT IS TENS?: Stands for "Transcutaneous Electrical Nerve Stimulation"- a safe, non-invasive, drug free method of pain relief used by Physical Therapists and prescribed Doctors for over 30 years. The iReliev Bundle delivers low-voltage pulses to the skin to stimulate nerve fibers effectively blocking the pain signal to your brain. Also increases natural endorphins--a natural pain reliever. name: China Premium Huang Shan Mao Feng Fur Peak Green Tea
short_summary: Features: The tea leaves used are picked up only in March, a period regarded as the best for this te
description: China Premium Huang Shan Mao Feng Fur Peak Green Tea  Features: The tea leaves used are picked up only in March, a period regarded as the best for this tea. It is made using the traditional processing method invented in Qing Dynasty. Shinny pale liquor with excellent clarity that tells the tea is indeed a high mountain plantation. Thick and "oily" liquor offers a 100% pure taste which is fresh and complex and yet delicate. Dry Leaves Appearance One bud and 1 to 2 tender leaves that hold a form of sparrow tongue. Even and strong apprearance shows pale green-yellow color. Fine hairs are obviously seen on the buds. Fragrance: Calm and delicate aroma from the dry leaves combined with a tiny smoky touch. Taste: The subtle and long fragrance is very pleasant in the cup. It gives an even more attractive fragrance when the liquor actually cools down. Freshness consistently shows along with the brewing combined with a pure and refreshing mouth feeling. The aftertaste is sweet and long lasting. Usage: Put 3-5 grams of tea leaves into a tea cup, add 85 degree Centigrade (185 Fahrenheit) boiled water, drink after a little while. Storage: Keep sealed in a cool and dry place, low temperature. Huang Shan Mao Feng is one of China Ten Famous Teas and originated in Anhui province during Qing Dynasty. It is an early spring green tea made of tender plump downy tips, skillfully crafted into a bird tongue shape with a flowery fragrance with a fresh sweet taste. The tea's fresh flowery fragrance and a smooth mellow taste makes it fit for a king. Name: Huang Shan Mao Feng, Yellow Mountain Fur Peak Great for Green Tea Weight LOSS self-help program!

name: Fitbit Aria WiFi Smart Scale
short_summary: Product description Totally different from your dad's old needle scale, the Fitbit Aria WiFi Smart S
description: Fitbit Aria WiFi Smart Scale  Product description Totally different from your dad's old needle scale, the Fitbit Aria WiFi Smart Scale uses advanced technology to track weight, lean mass, body fat percentage, and body mass index, allowing you to see all the numbers you need to start living a healthier lifestyle. With room for the storage of up to eight users, this scale recognizes who you are, displays your data, and sends your stats straight to your Fitbit account through your home's WiFi while remaining totally private to you. The sleek polished glass surface looks classy while resisting the condensation from steamy hot showers. Buying Guide Move it up: Since blood increases further up your arm, wear your tracker higher on your wrist to improve the heart rate signal during workouts. Start by moving the device up to three finger widths above your wrist bone, then experiment with slightly lower placement. Keep it secure: The less your tracker moves during exercise, the more chance you have of maintaining a heart rate signal throughout the activity. Do not wear the band too tightly, as this can restrict blood flow and goes against our wear and care guidelines. Hold steady for ten seconds: High intensity exercises or activities that cause you to keep your wrist bent (like push-ups) or move your arms vigorously (like dance) may interfere with heart rate signals. If you stop seeing a signal during these types of activities, hold your wrist steady for ten seconds during breaks to get your reading. Aria syncs automatically and wirelessly through your home WiFi network; Network requirements: Wireless 802.11b, WEP/WPA/WPA2 personal security, Automatic (DHCP) IP setup (static IP configuration not supported) Aria automatically recognizes up to eight different people; Your weight data syncs to your private Fitbit dashboard, so you can control what data you share; Measurement range: 20 to 350 pounds To set up for the first time, you’ll need one of the following: Windows XP and later, Mac OS X 10.5 and up, iPhone 4S and later, iPad 3 gen. and later, and leading Android and Windows devices Aria uses 4 AA batteries : no power cord necessary; Battery type: 4 standard 1.5 Volt size AA batteries (included); Works well and long with Polaroid AA batteries Water Resistance: Aria is designed to work in a humid bathroom environment; Some condensation due to hot showers, etc; will not damage the scale; The scale should not be submerged; Avoid splashing large amounts of water on the scale; To prevent slipping or accidents, please thoroughly dry the glass top and your feet before stepping on the scale

SUSTAINABLE PACKAGING – Our supplements are delivered in custom-made, reusable bottles made from recycled plastics. We also offer earth-friendly refill pouches made from plant-based materials. Using pouches to refill True Grace bottles minimizes our carbon footprint—and yours. Plus, every time you purchase a bottle or pouch of True Grace products, plastic is pulled out of the ocean through our partnership with ReSea Project. GOOD FOR YOU AND THE EARTH AROUND YOU - True Grace is rooted in the knowledge that comes with experience. With nearly 70 years of experience leading some of the top mission-driven companies in the natural products industry. We’re regenerating nutrition from the ground up through nutrient-dense supplements that strive to improve the health of body and planet. Have a supply handy while changing diapers to help keep your baby clean and fresh. For baby girls, while changing diapers, always wipe from front to back to minimize the amount of stool material that gets near her genitals. Also, be careful to clean all areas, as the folds in the skin around her genitals can hide urine and soil. How can I treat and prevent diaper rash? Red bumps on your baby's bottom may mean diaper rash. It can be caused by many factors, including leaving urine or bowel movement on the skin too long between changing diapers or even as a result of taking antibiotics. And when your baby starts solid foods, wait a few days between introducing each new food to see if the rash was caused by a particular food. If your baby has diaper rash, clean the entire diapered area gently but thoroughly with a baby wipe. It is also helpful to allow air to reach the skin. short_summary: Features: The tea leaves used are picked up only in March, a period regarded as the best for this te
description: 1st Grade Huangshang Maofeng Meidi Green Tea 50g Gift Tin  Features: The tea leaves used are picked up only in March, a period regarded as the best for this tea. It is made using the traditional processing method invented in Qing Dynasty. Shinny pale liquor with excellent clarity that tells the tea is indeed a high mountain plantation. Thick and "oily" liquor offers a 100% pure taste which is fresh and complex and yet delicate. Dry Leaves Appearance One bud and 1 to 2 tender leaves that hold a form of sparrow tongue. Even and strong apprearance shows pale green-yellow color. Fine hairs are obviously seen on the buds. Fragrance: Calm and delicate aroma from the dry leaves combined with a tiny smoky touch. Taste: The subtle and long fragrance is very pleasant in the cup. It gives an even more attractive fragrance when the liquor actually cools down. Freshness consistently shows along with the brewing combined with a pure and refreshing mouth feeling. The aftertaste is sweet and long lasting. Usage: Put 3-5 grams of tea leaves into a tea cup, add 85 degree Centigrade (185 Fahrenheit) boiled water, drink after a little while. Storage: Keep sealed in a cool and dry place, low temperature. 1st Grade Premium Huangshan Maofeng Green Tea 50g Gift Tin Huang Shan Mao Feng is one of China Ten Famous Teas and originated in Anhui province during Qing Dynasty. It is an early spring green tea made of tender plump downy tips, skillfully crafted into a bird tongue shape with a flowery fragrance with a fresh sweet taste. The tea's fresh flowery fragrance and a smooth mellow taste makes it fit for a king. A2AWorld Green Tea - The Way a Healthy Life Should Be !

description: Ivation Quad-Point Shiatsu Deep-Kneading Massage Pillow w/Switchable Heat – Relieves Muscle Tightness, Breaks up Muscle Knots, Relieves Back & Neck Aches – Lightweight, Portable & Powered by Wall Outlet  Like Your Personal Massage Therapist If you're too busy to go to the spa, have the spa come to you! The Ivation quad-point shiatsu deep-kneading massage pillow reimagines the delivery of a quality relaxing massage treatment. At a Price that's equal to - or possibly less than - the cost of a single Message therapy session with a live masseuse, this untiring, reliable, and ever-available personal device can provide a lifetime of therapy, relaxation, relief from aches and pains, as well as endless soothing indulgence. From your home to your car to your office, you'll never be too far away from a good knead, roll, rub, and pressure point release. Warmer Than the Best Human Hands Part of every good massage is undoubtedly the heat produced by all the energy of the focused motions. This warms the skin slightly and relaxes the area being treated. Ivation's shiatsu massage pillow incorporates this soothing feature by offering gentle heat that can be switched off independently of the massage nodes. What's nice about it is the fact that there are no fans or harsh blower modules; the heat is delivered steadily and gently at the skin surface by way of the massage nodes. The heat is automatically on upon massage start, and can be shut with the press of a button. Small footprint. Big helping hand. At just 12 inches long and a mere 4 inches at its thickest, this truly compact massage pillow goes anywhere the relaxation is needed. Its strategically sculpted design ensures a good fit in the small of your back and neck for aptly applied therapy. Dual rollers w/total of 4 nodes for a deep-kneading shiatsu massage that helps relax muscles and relieve tightness Neatly incorporated switchable heating function applies soothing warmth to skin, muscles, tendons & ligaments Features overheat protection with preprogrammed automatic shutoff after 20 minutes of continuous operation Slim, attractive profile in bean-shaped ergonomic design; perfect for back, neck, obliques, calves, and thighs Integrated elastic band to position on your chair's headrest; perfect for in-car use

description: Dream Dots for Spots, Acne Patches, Double Pack  For use at the night or during the day, Dream Dots can even be used under makeup. Absolutely! Dream Dots are formulated with safe, drug-free, non-irritating ingredients. In fact, Dream Dots are completely vegan, latex-free, and cruelty-free — so they’re suitable for all skin types. Of course, as with any new acne treatment, people with pre-existing skin conditions should consult their doctor before using Dream Dots. The secret is its patented hydrocolloid technology, which locks in moisture and helps blemishes heal 50% faster than dry healing. And because Dream Dots are completely drug-free, they will never dry out, sting, or irritate your skin. WHAT MAKES DREAM DOTS DIFFERENT FROM OTHER SPOT TREATMENTS? Dream Dots are unlike any other acne spot treatment because of their advanced hydrocolloid technology. This moist healing environment seals in skin-nourishing ingredients to soothe blemishes in hours and unlike other acne treatments, Dream Dots contain: No drugs No latex No parabens No fragrances or dyes No drying ingredients HOW DO DREAM DOTS WORK? Dream Dots are water-based, stick-on acne patches that adhere to skin and heal blemishes overnight. On contact with the pimple, the patented core locks in and absorbs the pore fluid. This creates a moist healing environment — leading to dramatically faster healing. Gently cleanse your face, then dry thoroughly. Center the Dream Dot over the affected area, then press down for 15 seconds. Leave on overnight (up to 10 hours). In the morning, remove the Dream Dot to see and feel the dramatic difference. description: Nerdwax Stop Slipping Glasses as Seen on Shark Tank  Nerdwax is a beeswax based blend of All Natural and Certified Organic Ingredientsspecially formulated to keep your glasses in place while you live your life. Q. WHAT ARE THE INGREDIENTS IN NERDWAX?A. We pride ourselves in our commitment to using only the best All-Natural Cosmetic Grade Ingredients.We use Certified Organic and Sustainably Sourced products whenever possible.Ingredients: Beeswax, Coconut Oil, Gum Rosin, Peppermint Oil Q. WILL NERDWAX MAKE MY SKIN BREAK OUT?A. Nerdwax is formulated with your skin in mind! It's made up of only the best Cosmetic Grade All-Natural and Certified Organic Ingredients. So, Not only is it great at keeping your glasses on your face, it is also great for your skin! Q. IS IT POSSIBLE TO BE ALLERGIC TO NERDWAX?A. All of the ingredients contained in Nerdwax are approved for cosmetic use. With that being said, as with any product that comes in contact with your skin it is possible to be allergic to one of the ingredients contained in nerdwax. It is always a good idea to test a product on the back of your hand or arm first if you think there may be risk of an allergic reaction. If you do experience an allergic reaction please discontinue use immediately, remove all nerdwax from your glasses, and consult your dermatologist. Q. HOW DO I APPLY NERDWAX?A. Simply roll the wax out of the tube and apply directly to the nosepads of your glasses. Q. HOW LONG WILL A SINGLE APPLICATION OF NERDWAX LAST?A. Nerdwax is worn off naturally by the facial oils produced by your skin.Application times can vary from 1-2 hours to a Full Day depending on how much you apply and what you are doing! Q. HOW LONG WILL A SINGLE TUBE OF NERDWAX LAST?A. Depending on the circumstances above... We estimate that you should get about 6-8 months out of a single tube! name: Hamamelis 200 organic tablets 400 mg
short_summary: The name Witch in witch-hazel has its origins in Middle English wiche, from the Old English wice, me
description: Hamamelis 200 organic tablets 400 mg  The name Witch in witch-hazel has its origins in Middle English wiche, from the Old English wice, meaning "pliant" or "bendable". "Witch hazel" was used in England as a synonym for Wych Elm, Ulmus glabra; American colonists simply extended the familiar name to the new shrub. The use of the twigs as divining rods, just as hazel twigs were used in England, may also have, by folk etymology, influenced the "witch" part of the name. The witch-hazels are deciduous shrubs or (rarely) small trees growing to 3–8 metres (9.8–26.2 ft) tall, rarely to 12 metres (39 ft) tall. The leaves are alternately arranged, oval, 4–16 centimetres (1.6–6.3 in) long and 3–11 centimetres (1.2–4.3 in) broad, with a smooth or wavy margin. The genus name, Hamamelis, means "together with fruit", referring to the simultaneous occurrence of flowers with the maturing fruit from the previous year. H. virginiana blooms in September-November while the other species bloom from January-March. Each flower has four slender strap-shaped petals 1–2 centimetres (0.39–0.79 in) long, pale to dark yellow, orange, or red. The fruit is a two-part capsule 1 centimetre (0.39 in) long, containing a single 5 millimetres (0.20 in) glossy black seed in each of the two parts; the capsule splits explosively at maturity in the autumn about 8 months after flowering, ejecting the seeds with sufficient force to fly for distances of up to 10 metres (33 ft), thus another alternative name "Snapping Hazel". Witch Hazel 200 Organic Tablets 400 mg Product of organic farming 2-3 tablets a day with a large glass of water during meals and as part of a balanced diet.

description: Taiping Houkui Green Tea 250g Gift Tin by A2AWorld Green Tea  Taiping Hou Kui (simplified Chinese: 太平猴魁; pinyin: tàipíng hóukuí lit. "peaceful monkey leader") tea is grown at the foot of Huangshan (黄山) in Taiping County, Anhui. The tea has been produced since the beginning of the 20th century and is produced around the small village of Hou Keng (猴坑). It won the "King of Tea" award in China Tea Exhibition 2004 and is China Famous Tea. The best Tai Ping Hou Kui is grown in the villages of Houkeng, Hougang and Yanjiachun. Teas produced in the surrounding areas are called by the same name, but costs much less.[1] It's renown for its "two knives and one pole": two straight leaves clasping the enormous bud with white hairs. The oven-made leaves are deep green in color with red veins underneath. The tea shoots can be as long as 15 centremeters. They are plucked from the Shi Da Cha, a large leaf-variety found only in Anhui Province.[1] Falsification is rampant. HOW TO USE: 1) Spray a 1 inch wide section of hair with water where you want the color streak to be. 2) Use the hair chalk to color on the wet section, starting at the root-Do not rub up and down. If you wish to use different colors, start with the lightest shade first, going from light to dark for best results. 3) Air dry hair completely. name: Premium Liuan Guapian Green Tea 250g Gift Pack
short_summary: Liu'an Guapian, also called Tea Pieces, is a special type of green tea and the only green tea in Chi
description: Premium Liuan Guapian Green Tea 250g Gift Pack  Liu'an Guapian, also called Tea Pieces, is a special type of green tea and the only green tea in China that requires no stalks or buds to be used in its production. After breaking off the leaves, rejecting the buds and stalks, a tea resembling the melon seeds in shape is made out of a unique traditional processing technology. The tea is produced in Liu'an, Jinzhai and Huoshan counties in Anhui Province. Since the three counties were under the governance of Liu'an Government Office in the past, the tea is thus named Liu'an Guapian, which was made a tribute tea. Liu'an Guapian has a long history and rich cultural connotation. It was recorded in the Tea Classics as early as in Tang Dynasty; in Ming Dynasty, the famous scientist Xu Guangqi praised highly of the tea in his work Nongzheng Quanshu (Complete Collection of Writings on Agriculture) as "the Liu'an Tea Pieces is the masterwork among all teas"; in early Qing Dynasty, it was listed among the tributes to the emperor, while in modern times it was specified as a special tribute tea for the Central Military Commission, which was loved by our first premier of PRC Zhou Enlai until the end of his life; in 1971 during the first visit of the former U.S. Secretary of State to China, the tea was presented as a national gift to our foreign friends. Liu'an Guapian is smooth, straight and regular in shape, with the leaf side rolling down in a smooth manner. Without buds or stalks, the leaves are similar to melon seeds in shape and assume the emerald green color, which are bright and sleek despite of a layer of white hair on the surface. The tea features clear liquid and a lingering scent, as well as a fresh, mellow and sweet aftertaste. description: Ovente Professional Salon Hair Dryer Stand 1000 Watts with Stainless Steel Heating Element and 3 Variable Speed Setting, Ionic Technology and Auto Shutoff 60 Minutes Timer, White (HDS223W)  Get that confidently beautiful “just left the salon” feeling—everyday!Equipped with a powerful 1000-Watt motor, Ovente hair dryers are not only powerful enough for professional use, they are also versatile and sleek in design. They are built with multiple features that reduce drying time while leaving your hair smooth, shiny, moisturized, healthy, and absolutely frizz-free. These include 1000-Watt power, dual-looped stainless steel heating element, a multi-bladed fan, and ionic technology. IONIC TECHNOLOGY helps hair break down water molecules by neutralizing positive (+) ions in the hair, reducing frizz and restoring a beautiful glow that makes your hair look hydrated and well-conditioned. This hair dryer stand is perfect for warming hair masks for optimum effectiveness, quickly drying all types of hair, and gentle styling that lasts. Now, you don’t have to go to the salon and spend money to look your most beautiful, you can do it all right in the comfort and convenience of your own home!***CAUTION: The air from this hair dryer blows upwards, so we STRONGLY urge customers to use a hair net, plastic cap, secure rollers, or any other form of hair security. FAILURE TO FOLLOW THIS INSTRUCTION WILL CAUSE YOUR HAIR TO BE SUCKED UP AND TANGLED INTO THE AIR HOLES.*** UPWARD AIRFLOW** – Gives hair lots of volume and prevents flatness while quickly and evenly drying hair. Make sure hair is PINNED DOWN AND COVERED by either a hair net or plastic cap so that hair won’t be sucked up and tangled into the air holes. 3-SPEED TURBO HAIR DRYING – Powered by a 120V/1000-Watt 3-Speed (low, med, high) dual-looped stainless steel heating element with a multi-bladed fan, Ovente’s Professional Hair Dryer Stand quickly and evenly dries your hair. No matter how long or thick, it gets the job done faster. description: DrFormulas Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder for Babies, Infants & Kids Probiotics with Saccharomyces Boulardii, L. Acidophilus, B. Infantis Better Than Gripe Water or Baby Drops, 30 Servings  Probiotics play and important role in supporting the growth and development of the immune system in babies, children, and kids. A probiotic supplement can help your children build up the healthy bacteria in their gut when they are young and growing and also contribute to their health later in life. DrFormulas Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder contains Lactobacillus acidophilus and Bifidobacterium infantis, two important probiotic strains which have been shown to reduce diarrhea and promote regular bowel movements. Your child deserves the best start in life, and DrFormulas can help you provide it. Advanced Formula: Nexabiotic contains a unique formula of 23 different strains of active probiotics, including Bifidobacterium lactis and Lactobacillus casei which improved defecation frequency and stool consistency in chronically constipated patients. Along with 21 other probiotic strains, this dietary supplement provides total support for digestive and immune health. Convenient Pre-Dosed Probiotic Powder in Capsules: Unlike unprotected probiotic powder that is exposed to air, Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder comes protected in pre-dosed capsules that are easily taken apart and emptied into food or drink. This is designed to make sure more beneficial bacteria reach your child’s gut to provide support for healthier, more regular bowel movements, and overall digestive and immune health. Gentle Enough for Babies: This Probiotic powder has been specially formulated for babies, children, and kids to include live probiotics with gentle action. It is flavorless and pre-dosed capsules so you can easily mix it with your child’s favorite foods and drinks. DrFormulas Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder for Babies and Infants provides a powerful boost of probiotics to your young child’s diet. Like all our products, it is made in the USA in a FDA inspected Good Manufacturing Practices facility. Your child's health and safety is our priority. Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder for Babies and Kids features prebiotic and the probiotics Saccharomyces boulardii, Lactobacillus acidophilus, and Bifidobacterium animalis lactis (formerly B. infantis), and 20 other probiotic strains. Nexabiotic Probiotic Powder in capsules are easy to take apart & mix in your kids' food & drinks. Flavorless so babies, infants & kids won't even know its there! Supports baby immune systems. Supports regular bowel movements and stools. Soothess & eases colic. Specially designed probiotic powder for infants, babies, toddlers, and kids. Provides a potent boost of probiotics and prebiotics to your baby's diet. More CFUs and probiotics than gripe water and probiotic drops. Made in the USA in a FDA inspected NSF GMP facility. Your child's safety is our priority.

The Original Natural Spectrum Floor Lamp by Verilux, Inc. Often Imitated, Never Duplicated Backed by 50 Years of Research The Verilux Original Natural Spectrum Floor Lamp is a delight for sore eyes. It not only provides the best of natural daylight indoors, but it also helps eliminate glare, eyestrain, and fatigue. This versatile and practical lamp uses patented technology to sharpen vision with greater contrast and true color vibrancy. Flicker Elimination Technology provides steady illumination while its Parabolic Grid Diffuser shields your eyes from glare, making reading, crafting, painting, and other visually demanding tasks more enjoyable and easier to perform for longer periods of time. The flexible gooseneck allows you to direct light right where you need it most or cast broader lighting for an entire area. With an advanced electronic ballast system, Verilux lamps provide greater light output with less energy usage. You get 150-watts of comparable incandescent brightness using only 27 watts of energy, so your bulb lasts longer, creating less waste and more savings for you. Scientifically Tuned to the Human Eye The back of the human eye has light receptors, called cones and rods, located in the retina. Cones respond to different color wavelengths and rods handle depth perception and contrast. Under typical interior lights, the rods and cones are not well stimulated, which can cause visual fatigue. With the Verilux Original Natural Spectrum Floor Lamp, the eye responds more efficiently, improving comprehension, productivity, and focus. About Verilux, Inc. Founded in 1956, Verilux, Inc., the "Healthy Lighting Company," is a pioneer in the design and manufacture of lifestyle products utilizing Natural Spectrum lighting technology. The company offers a wide range of high quality home, office, and travel products engineered to improve vision, help alleviate the symptoms associated with seasonal light change, aid in sleeping, sanitize surfaces without the use of chemicals, and clear and rejuvenate the skin. Verilux, which is Latin for "true light," is committed to supporting balanced and healthy lifestyles that benefit everyone and the world around us. Verilux calls this "life in a better light." And there are good reasons for that.  Jojoba oil is a botanical oil and just like vitamin e its makeup is so similar to the oil (sebum) your body naturally produces and no wonder it has a concentration of vitamin e. We’ve included VITAMIN C, another antioxidant that helps with free-radicals and stimulate collagen production to decrease the appearance of FINE LINES, SCARS & STRETCH MARKS. Combining Vitamin E & C speeds up the mending procedure of the skin. Mother Nature's Essentials products are always fresh. We produce all our products on demand so it aways fresh.
